00:21:37.138 --> 00:21:39.130
but we always end up fighting.

00:21:39.130 --> 00:21:42.941
When she called this afternoon,
we had the same argument as always.

00:21:42.941 --> 00:21:47.357
It's like we're not a part
of each other's lives anymore.

00:21:47.357 --> 00:21:49.463
It feels like...

00:21:49.463 --> 00:21:53.578
we're only together... in our relationship status.

00:21:55.900 --> 00:21:59.060
I can't even give you advice on this one, man.

00:21:59.750 --> 00:22:03.170
I've never been in a relationship
like yours before.

00:22:09.670 --> 00:22:11.270
Hey.

00:22:12.010 --> 00:22:13.793
Don't worry about it on my account.

00:22:13.793 --> 00:22:16.470
I'm sure that once we see each other again,

00:22:16.470 --> 00:22:18.372
things will get better on their own.

00:22:18.372 --> 00:22:19.736
Hey.

00:22:19.736 --> 00:22:21.430
Cheers.

00:22:23.330 --> 00:22:25.930
Well, I hope you're right.

00:22:39.590 --> 00:22:41.100
Hey, hey.

00:22:41.100 --> 00:22:43.060
Easy there.

00:22:45.850 --> 00:22:47.490
Mind your own business.

00:22:56.790 --> 00:22:59.890
[Full & a Half Koh Khen]

00:23:14.610 --> 00:23:18.110
[Yesterday - Phana: I have something
I want to talk about.]

00:23:28.120 --> 00:23:29.820
The bar isn't open yet.

00:23:29.820 --> 00:23:33.160
Right now, we're only serving breakfast and coffee.

00:23:33.160 --> 00:23:36.843
I'm not here for a drink. I'm here to see P'Timmy.

00:23:37.827 --> 00:23:41.178
Timmy isn't at the bar. Is there something you need?

00:23:41.178 --> 00:23:43.420
I'm supposed to start
my internship here tomorrow,

00:23:43.420 --> 00:23:46.284
and P'Timmy told me to come meet the owner first.

00:23:46.284 --> 00:23:48.760
Oh.

00:23:48.760 --> 00:23:50.570
- Hey, Ai Ping.
- Oh, P'Timmy.

00:23:50.570 --> 00:23:53.119
Sorry I'm late. It was a rough night.

00:23:53.119 --> 00:23:56.410
P'Phana, this is the young guy I told you about, the one interning at the bar.

00:23:56.410 --> 00:23:58.345
Yeah, I figured.

00:23:58.345 --> 00:24:01.504
He didn't give you any trouble, did he?

00:24:01.504 --> 00:24:02.935
Give me trouble?

00:24:02.935 --> 00:24:05.803
A moment ago, he looked like a lost kid
who'd just wandered in.

00:24:05.803 --> 00:24:09.490
So, what part of the business
are you interested in?

00:24:09.490 --> 00:24:11.319
I want to learn about the bar operations.

00:24:11.319 --> 00:24:12.760
And to be honest, the reason I came here

00:24:12.760 --> 00:24:16.320
is to understand how a hybrid
restaurant and bar like this works.

00:24:18.110 --> 00:24:22.700
Alright, I'll have Nava and Timmy
train you on the bar side of things.

00:24:22.700 --> 00:24:25.380
- Got it, Phi.
- And when there's time,

00:24:25.380 --> 00:24:27.780
I'll teach you the operation side myself.

00:24:27.780 --> 00:24:30.550
Oh, but when the bar gets busy,

00:24:30.550 --> 00:24:32.968
you'll probably have to help serve tables.

00:24:32.968 --> 00:24:34.830
I'd be happy to.

00:24:37.043 --> 00:24:39.392
Okay, I'll leave him with you guys.

00:24:39.392 --> 00:24:41.190
- Got it, Phi.
- I've got to get back to my work.

00:24:41.190 --> 00:24:43.970
- Come on, follow me. I'll show you the bar.
- Okay.

00:26:09.587 --> 00:26:11.490
Hello?

00:26:12.737 --> 00:26:14.350
Hello?

00:26:15.010 --> 00:26:17.181
What's up, Phana?

00:26:17.181 --> 00:26:20.842
Yeah, I'm outside your house now. I brought your car.

00:26:20.842 --> 00:26:23.706
Hey, is my car ready already?

00:26:23.706 --> 00:26:26.850
Yep. Come on out and get your vehicle, sir.

00:26:26.850 --> 00:26:29.600
Okay, okay, I'm coming down now.

00:26:44.362 --> 00:26:45.413
Phana.

00:26:45.413 --> 00:26:46.564
Hey.

00:26:46.564 --> 00:26:49.480
- Here's your car.
-

00:26:49.480 --> 00:26:52.037
- I checked it all over for you.
- You asshole.

00:26:52.037 --> 00:26:54.480
Not a single scratch on it.

00:26:54.480 --> 00:26:56.310
Thanks a lot.

00:26:56.310 --> 00:27:00.741
So, how was your first night
sleeping in a new place?

00:27:00.741 --> 00:27:02.192
Not bad.

00:27:02.192 --> 00:27:05.253
Switching from a condo to a house
actually feels pretty good.

00:27:05.253 --> 00:27:07.584
That's good to hear. A change of scenery is nice.

00:27:07.584 --> 00:27:09.420
You might end up liking it.

00:27:09.420 --> 00:27:13.851
- Phana.
- Oh, Nava. What are you doing here?

00:27:13.851 --> 00:27:17.020
Auntie Pha asked me to bring Phurich
the documents you forgot.

00:27:17.020 --> 00:27:18.803
Oh, thanks a lot.

00:27:18.803 --> 00:27:20.610
Thanks.

00:27:21.740 --> 00:27:25.280
I was thinking of driving around town today.

00:27:25.280 --> 00:27:27.790
Would you like to be my guide?

00:27:33.897 --> 00:27:36.210
I'm not available today.

00:27:36.210 --> 00:27:38.400
He took the day off.

00:27:39.330 --> 00:27:41.290
Why is he taking the day off?

00:27:42.126 --> 00:27:44.074
You don't need to know everything.

00:27:44.074 --> 00:27:46.186
He requested this day off many days ago.

00:27:46.186 --> 00:27:48.046
But if a member of my staff
is taking time off,

00:27:48.046 --> 00:27:50.210
shouldn't I know about it?

00:27:51.792 --> 00:27:54.540
Well, I'll be going now, Phana.

00:27:54.540 --> 00:27:55.580
Ride safely.

00:27:55.580 --> 00:27:57.100
- I will. See you.
- Bye.

00:27:57.100 --> 00:27:58.590
Bye.

00:28:02.414 --> 00:28:04.163
You, seriously...

00:28:04.163 --> 00:28:05.860
Right in front of me, no less.

00:28:05.860 --> 00:28:09.173
If you're just trying to play games, go play them with someone else.

00:28:09.173 --> 00:28:11.050
Not Nava.

00:28:11.050 --> 00:28:12.530
And if I'm not playing games?

00:28:12.530 --> 00:28:14.990
Does that mean I'm allowed to pursue him?

00:28:18.140 --> 00:28:19.920
Someone like you?

00:28:19.920 --> 00:28:22.027
You shouldn't even say things like that.

00:28:22.027 --> 00:28:24.760
Well, since I'm here,

00:28:24.760 --> 00:28:27.309
give me a ride to the bar.

00:28:27.309 --> 00:28:30.230
Also, an intern is starting
at the bar tomorrow.

00:28:30.230 --> 00:28:32.940
He's all yours. I don't like training people.

00:28:32.940 --> 00:28:34.980
You handle it.

00:28:34.980 --> 00:28:37.692
Fine. In that case,
you can keep an eye on the customers

00:28:37.692 --> 00:28:40.250
and handle the front-of-house for me.

00:28:40.960 --> 00:28:42.460
Let's go.

00:30:39.170 --> 00:30:43.090
I'd advise you not to touch that.

00:30:47.260 --> 00:30:49.887
Forgive my rudeness.

00:30:49.887 --> 00:30:53.318
I just saw that it was beautiful, so I...

00:30:53.318 --> 00:30:55.590
That's precisely the reason.

00:30:55.590 --> 00:31:01.905
Its beauty is what lures humans who are full of greed, time and time again.

00:31:03.059 --> 00:31:04.920
What do you mean?

00:31:05.890 --> 00:31:07.620
Never mind.

00:31:07.620 --> 00:31:12.990
Let's just say it's a personal possession of mine,
and very valuable.

00:31:13.824 --> 00:31:17.480
By the way, what kind of fish
does this scale come from?

00:31:17.480 --> 00:31:19.580
I've never seen anything like it before.

00:31:20.950 --> 00:31:26.270
If I told you it was a merman's scale, would you believe me?

00:31:27.886 --> 00:31:30.090
I'd have to be crazy to believe that.

00:31:30.760 --> 00:31:33.020
It's good that you don't believe it.

00:31:33.020 --> 00:31:36.190
Because the more people
who believe in these things,

00:31:36.190 --> 00:31:40.050
the more that bad things always seem to follow.

00:31:42.260 --> 00:31:45.150
You're not a tourist, are you?

00:31:45.150 --> 00:31:46.620
No.

00:31:46.620 --> 00:31:49.330
But you're not from this island, either.

00:31:49.330 --> 00:31:51.800
I just recently decided to move here.

00:31:51.800 --> 00:31:54.149
I'm partners with a friend
in a bar we opened.

00:31:54.149 --> 00:31:56.390
I'm also looking for a place to build a resort

00:31:56.390 --> 00:31:58.780
and planning to stay here for the long haul.

00:31:59.500 --> 00:32:03.460
There should only be two types of people
on Koh Khen:

00:32:03.460 --> 00:32:06.670
one, the people who are originally from here,

00:32:06.670 --> 00:32:09.480
and two, tourists.

00:32:09.480 --> 00:32:13.820
This island is no place
for newcomers to settle down.

00:32:15.640 --> 00:32:17.530
Why is that?

00:32:25.680 --> 00:32:27.710
Excuse me.

00:32:30.949 --> 00:32:33.298
Yeah, Phana?

00:32:33.298 --> 00:32:35.360
Okay, I'm on my way.

00:32:42.990 --> 00:32:45.470
I have to go now.

00:32:45.470 --> 00:32:48.370
Again, my apologies for being rude.

00:32:51.420 --> 00:32:53.774
May I ask your name?

00:32:53.774 --> 00:32:55.650
Silp.

00:32:56.390 --> 00:32:58.290
My name is Phurich.

00:32:58.290 --> 00:33:00.030
My bar is on the main beach.

00:33:00.030 --> 00:33:02.290
It's called Full & a Half.

00:33:02.290 --> 00:33:06.230
If you ever want to get a drink, please stop by.

00:33:06.230 --> 00:33:08.531
It was nice to meet you.

00:33:08.531 --> 00:33:10.320
Likewise.

00:33:15.100 --> 00:33:17.160
I'll be on my way now.

00:34:03.325 --> 00:34:05.847
Nava, I'm outside the house.

00:34:05.847 --> 00:34:09.430
Okay, Phraphai. I'll be right out.

00:34:10.148 --> 00:34:13.290
Take your time. Come out whenever you're ready.

00:34:13.290 --> 00:34:14.770
Got it.

00:34:14.770 --> 00:34:16.140
Okay.

00:34:19.139 --> 00:34:22.939
Take your time getting ready. I can wait.

00:34:22.939 --> 00:34:25.047
And as for your heart,
I can wait for that, too.

00:34:25.047 --> 00:34:28.920
No matter how long it takes,
I'll wait for you, Nava.

00:34:28.920 --> 00:34:30.440
Met.

00:34:30.440 --> 00:34:33.550
You're just trying to hitch a ride
so we can go shed our toxins, aren't you?

00:34:33.550 --> 00:34:36.610
Hey, I was just teasing you a little.
No need to get upset.

00:34:36.610 --> 00:34:38.446
Watch what you say.

00:34:38.446 --> 00:34:41.190
I don't want Nava to find out about this.

00:34:42.058 --> 00:34:43.199
To be honest,

00:34:43.199 --> 00:34:46.560
I think everyone on this island already knows how you feel about Nava.

00:34:46.560 --> 00:34:50.180
He's the only one who still sees you
as just a kind older brother.

00:34:50.180 --> 00:34:51.511
Let me ask you seriously.

00:34:51.511 --> 00:34:54.230
Do you have any plans at all
to tell him how you feel?

00:34:54.230 --> 00:34:55.521
You're all adults now.

00:34:55.521 --> 00:34:57.980
If you feel something for someone, just say it.

00:35:00.020 --> 00:35:01.907
Oh, hey, Met.

00:35:01.907 --> 00:35:03.640
Are you coming with us today?

00:35:03.640 --> 00:35:07.360
My car is having some trouble, so I'm just going to hitch a ride.

00:35:08.140 --> 00:35:11.780
Nava. Should we get going?

00:35:11.780 --> 00:35:13.020
I'm ready.

00:35:13.020 --> 00:35:15.640
Let's see.

00:35:21.050 --> 00:35:22.900
Lost in a daydream, huh?

00:35:26.690 --> 00:35:28.360
What was that?

00:35:29.779 --> 00:35:31.560
Met is just talking nonsense, Nava.

00:35:31.560 --> 00:35:33.050
Come on, let's go.

00:35:33.050 --> 00:35:34.550
Okay.

00:35:34.550 --> 00:35:35.970
Let's go.

00:35:43.290 --> 00:35:46.482
If you're going to be like that,
you two could have just gone by yourselves.

00:35:46.482 --> 00:35:48.390
I guess I'll shed my toxins here.

00:35:52.325 --> 00:35:55.680
Hey! Phraphai, Nava, wait for me!

00:36:13.820 --> 00:36:15.590
The weather is great today.

00:36:15.590 --> 00:36:18.050
After we shed our toxins, I'm going to swim for a bit longer.

00:36:18.050 --> 00:36:19.450
Okay.

00:36:19.450 --> 00:36:22.570
You're not in a hurry to be anywhere,
are you, Nava?

00:36:22.570 --> 00:36:23.770
No.

00:36:23.770 --> 00:36:26.490
I'd like to swim a little longer, too.

00:36:27.390 --> 00:36:29.750
Alright, I'm heading in first.
See you down there.

00:36:29.750 --> 00:36:31.510
Okay, see you in a bit.

00:37:55.320 --> 00:37:57.740
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:37:57.740 --> 00:37:59.840
- Make yourselves at home.
- Thank you.

00:38:02.024 --> 00:38:03.440
Hello.

00:38:03.440 --> 00:38:05.580
If you need anything, please let us know.

00:38:05.580 --> 00:38:06.900
Make yourselves comfortable.

