I'm hitting on you.

00:42:58.778 --> 00:43:00.510
Are you here to eat?

00:43:00.510 --> 00:43:01.570
No.

00:43:01.570 --> 00:43:03.750
Someone I'm close with works here.

00:43:03.750 --> 00:43:05.650
You mean Nava?

00:43:05.650 --> 00:43:07.826
If you can see a crash coming,

00:43:07.826 --> 00:43:10.270
I'd suggest you back off now.

00:43:10.270 --> 00:43:12.500
Because there's no insurance
that will cover this.

00:43:12.500 --> 00:43:14.650
By the way, have either of you

00:43:14.650 --> 00:43:17.280
heard the rumors about humans
coming to hunt merfolk on our island?

00:43:17.280 --> 00:43:20.010
Den, where did you hear that from?

00:43:20.010 --> 00:43:24.180
Nava, I don't want you to trust any human,
you understand?

00:43:24.180 --> 00:43:26.250
Ping, are you from this island?

00:43:26.250 --> 00:43:29.640
Why do you ask? Do I not look like I'm from here?

00:43:30.440 --> 00:43:32.261
I think...

00:43:32.261 --> 00:43:34.100
I saw something last night.

00:43:34.100 --> 00:43:36.220
